amphetamine and ethanol interactions in humans." Clin Pharmacol Ther 57 (1995): 559-68[9] "Product Information. Didrex (benzphetamine)" Pharmacia and Upjohn, Kalamazoo, MI.[10] "Product Information. Suprenza (phentermine)." Akrimax Pharmaceuticals, Cranford, NJ.', 1767363022);
